init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This new collective mind, called the Consciousness, is a remarkable phenomenon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But it is also a weapon that can give humanity the edge it needs to drive back the Ethereal invaders.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Using the Consciousness as a weapon, they begin to fight back against those who would see them destroyed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They strike at the same times in every location and hit the Ethereals where they least expect it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But it does not finish them off.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have to work together to survive.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But it is not without great cost.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Humans are a much smaller population now.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Without children in the future, the Consciousness would be even stronger.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: These two sides go to war.
